‚Ä¢ overlooking view of manila bay and moa eye
‚Ä¢ alfresco dining only, best to come at night","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9c9O0JCnIYGUiuNhAXhCteGUZlfU5DgIXAYXy"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Floyser Ricafrente","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXampog85MkNUjDQogXmZaBQIbesV4eLUJg0tDvYrahQrfG3f_HlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Decently priced coffee for its quality and well placed location. Definitely one of the most aesthetically pleasing cafe in SM MOA and a must try. One of its best hours is near sunset since the heat from the sun isn't that intense and it gives you an amazing view of the sunset.

Coffee is a bit strong but in a good way especially for the Mallow and toasted chips frappe. The white mocha frappe does mellow down the strength of the coffee, but it is still present in the overall flavor.

There was a small hiccup with our order when we specifically ordered "White Mocha Iced" but what we got was "Frappe White Mocha" we wondered why the price was different from what was on the menu.

Overall a great place to have a chat and great coffee without breaking the bank, and would come by again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMp4JAdrOTIxladc0XcqiXakrNgbpxP5fXSBOT5"],"When":"2023-4-9"},{"Name":"Karl Macariza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4X2w7qSjkx0OGMjFwm-EFAdq2tODkF2aXvFke9KGqm_QoFPYf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A nice cafe in a great location. I saw the cafe while strolling around the seaside area of MOA and decided to try it because the exterior and ambiance looked very nice and unique to the area. good for taking Instagram pictures (especially at night or in the afternoon).

The staff were very polite and friendly. They do inform you of what is available or not before ordering. The downside is that the service is quite slow. We waited more than 20 minutes for our drinks and food. It might just be because the place is quite full, though.

Food offerings are quite limited. The only available at that time was this Oreo cheesecake type of cake (not sure of the name). The taste is pleasantly sweet. I ordered a non-coffee-based drink with chocolate chips on it. It's quite good and can quench your thirst.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNakq9Yk6R_ADfUS5lo13mU84Qn04btZw1_wQtW"],"When":"2022-8-8"},{"Name":"KevUn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcLDNcKF9IKhlVmsy6bXfZpleERCJJI-8sJabcfgavIIjvTC2YdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you are tired of the mainstream coffee chains, this is the place to go. title: Yardstick Coffee | MOA Square

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"joshua garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7c89Ij-OX1NO6kY9Oqd6bPa-4BOoPY4w46-PZ8l826jvMxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Place is always packed, and trying to get a seat is difficult and stressful. People also tend to stay here to have a good chat and relax, but being in MOA that seems to be difficult since it gets pretty loud. You can also come to take a couple of pictures and go but price is not what one would say "cheap". Also, not all menus were available and they only tell you this after you waited for 20 or 30 minutes to order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1tAbFYdVfCxct90dPs7yTo0vV1m4C3LL8dH3f"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Shai Bungcag","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3WHRVLycXgNDOb70AJ-HRdpOAL-W_wIK9AXCo0xXEHImvS-fh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Finally got to try their coffee and opted for the vanilla latte. The coffee tastes great, just like I wanted. It's not too sweet or bitter, just the right balance. The place is comfortable with a nice view, though it tends to get noisy since it's near the mall entrances.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcxNOjXd_MRhmZaVeShU_xJXGcP3Y4Epvj3HeU"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Ate girl Noodles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKUeBhEPiQH6OmXtYVOxUozsBnqj0EvDbHuQgEKpKc2utahnhsQw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Seating is limited. There's a view into the outside of the building but there's an SMDC ad that's an eyesore, blocking what would be an okay view.  It's still mostly pretty with the wooden furniture and wooden blocks from the ceiling, the occasional cement texture and the tiled bar. The ambient lighting adds to the overall look of the place.

Service is fast. I ordered a small iced latte, and it was okay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0c2sBO8VEDhGKtvUbX4YfmzVPunhMaWSDQsjA"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"John Jeremiah Gozum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaCjHMIJK0P599ZTK5kqqL8R1UVN9xILluhoWUIfbYnyouozY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food:
Sea Salt Latte - Coffee was amazing. Sea salt top balanced all the sweetness, coffee flavor, and the milk. Price is steep. Best consumed without the straw. Must try.

Service:
- Quick
- Has a fob to alert when order is ready
- Self service for service water, straws, and cup covers

Atmosphere:
- Modern cafe vibe
- Has an obstructed view of the MOA Eye
- Place isn't that cold
- Cafe is open, expect noise

Verdict:
Coffee is amazing. Service is very good. Atmosphere is mid. Must try for the coffee.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOe-bjkw7bbak32ZYzsDNz0giw2GqXSJzh8sYa"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"V Angel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKagoiXTHP7Ni5DmS2oMj_sE7NRv1nksC4gJI8UCMUZ0iNKn2ZV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Coffee: Bland and not good

Food: Waffle Matcha was underwhelming. The Waffle I was expecting was somehow crunchy on outside, it was not. It was just soggy. The cream was not good either.

Atmosphere: their AC was broken, some seats were hot coz of the broken ac.

Staff: aloof and not courteous. Although it was very straightforward, I was probably used to other coffee shops that the staff at the cashier was somehow warm and courteous.

Value for money : expensive for a bland taste of coffee.

Verdict: Not worth your time. Not coming back. All the hype was literally just hype. Not good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNijMnlCv1ij58IR16jXf9ms-R8ntyDZN5klZle"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"Sarah J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdYAG5MbT1VgK6p-0tMBer3pvB6MQ65q5Rpjqgo6VNRv8KO-vm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time to visit and it was a bit hard to find as we aren‚Äôt frequent MOA visitors.

Sea Salt Latte was yummy, Matcha Latte wasn‚Äôt to my liking though. Small space, few tables available for seating so it can get a bit crowded. If you want to drink in peace, visit as soon as they open at 10am. That‚Äôs what we did. No waiting time at all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNG6ZV4FJ644_QoHCpYo_gKwloIOASO3BFN9y-"],"When":"2024-5-25"},{"Name":"Jimi There","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHry-7fqjV3LHeI9FWMpcLqiOVwSN3e45PF27u9-OjQuhtsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Coffee with a nice view.
As a tourist, it was so hard to find this place. I had to ask for direction to Ikea to gradually find the way to this place.
This place has the view of the MOA Eye. The space is small but cozy and warm.
There is limited space so you may have to wait a while to have a seat (especially the one opposite the ferris wheel). Service is normal (self serve self clean).
As for the drink, I ordered a Manila latte. The coffee was good but sour pineapple slushies does not go well with it, feel watery. Not to mention I expected more natural, fresher pineapple. Too bad for a signature drink.
Plus point is this place accepts Apple Pay, though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIekr2dVZV6RJZpJbj4PKDivtUX2RU1rmwF2cO"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Floyser Ricafrente","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXampog85MkNUjDQogXmZaBQIbesV4eLUJg0tDvYrahQrfG3f_HlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee with a great scenic view of the MOA Eye

A wide enough range of coffee and milk based drinks. They do also offer pastries and bread. They use plastic cups for their iced based products making it more presentable and aesthetic.

Their cafe is well placed where whenever the sun is out at sunset, the light hits the cafe just right to make it a lot scenic and aesthetic. Although it was a bit warm in the shop due to it being close to the entrance of the mall.

The staff were nice and talkative to give you information about their drinks and such. They also were kind enough to refill my tumbler with water.

Overall a great cafe would definitely come by again in the future and try out their other drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhCUlznk9Qx6neK8pcux4tbBfTacToQQSrY_gL"],"When":"2023-8-9"}]

[{"Name":"Fatima Grace Abad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVm_lvF-XFKU3DG2DmzFStUqEwDh0YOUQmJJ3yrttLW12UvDkcp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coffee here slaps! If you are a coffee person, this place is great. They don‚Äôt have much else available in terms of food or snacks, but Vietnamese coffee and tea options here are great. They also have Vietnamese sandwiches available, though they are kind of dry and not really too my taste. They have great seating options to hang out with friends or a date. They also have a bathroom here, plus power sockets on the floors and walls.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeun4J0DdpprB_PMdmyOOE3Ft0Ri2ciBo7tNI"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Gilbz D.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZ-9c0U20H84_fqgALfCB0ppA2iLvuur-QQJq9Q8YC8QSF4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Vietnamese coffee/tea house in Double Dragon complex, Pasay, where one can read, web-browse or meet friends. Few choices of banh-mi sandwiches (p119); espresso coffee (p89/105/109); cold/hot tea choices: lychee/milk/peach); pastries: brownies, cookies, muffins (p39-89). I enjoyed my hot lychee tea.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN175BAO54qKrdjoylRRcNFzorDHNzD5lOMTQQI"],"When":"2024-10-17"},{"Name":"MrsWayfarer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtR3dIZLKzoN0mJzM8etgK9dTPYFRjFK9P-rhz2TOC_kxHDhJC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Good coffee and service. The pastries were also good - not too sweet. Plenty of seats, and the cafe was spacious. Will try their banh mi next time.

Update, May 2023: went back here because we liked it the first time, however we were disappointed by the change. It was hot inside, their airconditioning was not working and they did not even have fans. The queue took so long, and the wait for our coffee and cookies took even longer. And to top the disappointment: they served us cookies with splashes of coffee on them. If it was not for another guest I think who called their attention they would not even replace it. This cafe now lacks customer service. I hope their management does something about it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4LUcFUAGqbsmB_4mTYpb5dyV4bfeuV6FqpQU5"],"When":"2022-6-26"},{"Name":"Rommel Lagmay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXZ2KsNvRALNXTNo-IY8ukJhTPXAL00TyNg-_EkNEeQW9fzNj-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Excellent service.

Great tasking coffee.

Friendly staff.

There are power outlets so you can charge your gadgets.

But when I went there early this morning, there was a group of people who were shouting all the time. Not sure if they were drunk or high on drugs or plain rowdy. They were inconsiderate. I‚Äôm not sure if they were a regular customer of this coffee shop but if you want peace and quiet, this may not be your kind of place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marco Gosalvez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNjMFqPF6C8l8f4whfGM5w2YNyANBq77ZYpQgi0zZOGtJpMG7o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The bread was not crunchy enough. Other times the bread was soft and not crumbly. Iced coffee was so full of ice and the coffee was only part half full. Appears unappealing. Inconsistent at best because last time they served it properly. Service staff and duty supervisor attitudes appear unwelcoming. They appear to be too busy to care for customers. Lastly, the dining area atmosphere was ruined because the counter staff are too noisy. I wouldn't mind the noise of the equipment but their voices while communicating were too loud. All the service staff wore face masks except the supervisor who never even once smiled even to customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPCyP27B4zST7V8VA9HI3riGC2UQhCfO7WZtT0"],"When":"2023-7-17"},{"Name":"Jƒ´n Aranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpAsNI5EWrKGMY51oQRVCYoiMHkaXppwFVqxFjH9fgBq465_VK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Their staff here are terrible, they don't even know how to smile to customer even their manager! At least improve the quality of your customer service. It's a shame that the coffee is delicious but can't be appreciated because of the attitude of the staff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoLL619YRHjIcDufgZ6coLdWnvyZ8PBsZDB2xY"],"When":"2023-9-8"},{"Name":"Fritz Jason Villareal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZCs6DGPQJO560NWeBvGefb-QPT2SWau14d2kPmPNogossrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Their coffee is great, and the best part is that this place is open 24/7, so you can visit anytime. Just a heads up, it can feel hot and humid inside because the aircon isn't running at full power.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kath G.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvojPsEpvhpWx4W8WbgRh5hZPwBIvBSUSUDrk1vvf4vfeJHlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"When we visited, there were not much to choose from. Sadly, there were no cakes available but there were cookies, cup cakes, and muffins. Banh mis are also available. I like the jellies on the coffee tho. The ambience is good. The food is affordable too. This is a best place to relax and take some time with an order of coffee.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCmnlYgqkbgPizDmWQ1eyF9p6elFuyzlQpM0XJ"],"When":"2023-3-14"}]

[{"Name":"Rommel Lagmay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXZ2KsNvRALNXTNo-IY8ukJhTPXAL00TyNg-_EkNEeQW9fzNj-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The place is filthy.
Trash all over the place.
Nobody was cleaning tables and all leftovers by previous customers were kept untouched.
And it took them a long time to prepare the drinks though not so many guests were inside the store.
No greetings from the staff whatsoever.

As expected, drinks were so-so and it‚Äôs very expensive!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOctva3Q9LqfmkFAjWiihXfJjfq6Wxc3-Z2gIlz"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"COCO&LYCHEE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUP6Gs2WQFkVJmbCXpHSiY1eVBZauRW9N3vDBLQ-UJ2MTPIgK6q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Thanks Frenzy

I  had what a surprise experience never had before from this coffee shop.
Before I had good experience but today whose name is Frenzy? When I got here she‚Äôs the only one employee here and she was doing do the dishes so I didn‚Äôt wanna interrupt her so I waited until she‚Äôs done with.

And eventually she noticed me I was waiting for ordering and she seemed like she annoyed by something but it was okay. I know what she felt cuz I‚Äôve done with that situation.

But then I was waiting to get my changes by my hand which were a few of coins but she just dropped the coins on the cashier table.

I‚Äôm like what is wrong with her?
So I gave her 1 peso in the tip box and got out from this coffee shop and she kept looking at me even though I already left.
I hope she learned it why I gave her 1 peso.

Thanks for your unpleasant service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eizen Barleta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwKxq6J9WB1d9jGuLq6SNyjw_6v5hZM3w7nGaBwbPJy9INxxKoSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A lot of cafes in this part of Manila lacks that serenity you‚Äôd want for a coffee shop. It‚Äôll be a great snack spot after watching a movie in the mall.

The place is well maintained and the staff members attend to your needs immediately.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-dnCjLXVmzf8UVPKmyT3IqR-sKyCa_I9u08Ml"],"When":"2022-3-14"},{"Name":"Superbomby man","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJIbgOzxjFVDOzOLgOatAMWhlDL9AfF15jKcCWfkdW-JDk-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Location is good. Well lit ambiance and organize tables, lots of fresh pastry and drinks to choose from, great coffee shop experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPzSXRRaWJN7cU4VlFiD8LbW4hNgSAlfONhxdy"],"When":"2023-5-25"},{"Name":"Bernardo Andico (Neb)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXm1IR8qsdi6fUq_wz5o0saL9i6HVXnw5VTuljyXWMv9V2aKGM0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fast becoming my favorite coffee shop!

Definitely a place to visit regularly!

Superhighly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"La Viajera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKac4EiYA7sjRCOymQdLt6p7uq8a8q9IstNL4kE9z1HpShRiA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved the atmosphere when I visited. CBTL at S Maison is a place where you can sit quietly with your laptop if you need to study or do some work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angel Genesis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVL522lU2IiYe6NJ_DvJxLaOPK-r6YTkzF66eZjz-B89bwbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Went there with my 2 kids at 5 pm for late merienda since my kids already hungry na..

i been waiting. And waiting. .

NO DRINKS ARRIVED

But that will be my first and last sa BRANCH nila","Images":null,"When":""}]

As she telling us that any foods from outside is not allowed in their dine-in policy. Like, I can understand if we don‚Äôt buy anything and we sit their just for fun, but hello!we ordered some beverages even it is  pricey. So we dont have any choice, we decided to-go option.People have options of what they want to order or eat. If they just ordered some drinks, It‚Äôs fine as long as they paid any amount of money in your store to sit in. Change that guideline or policy of your store, God bless!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIilymfn67PmWBhYmhK1jA6wPDzxgCQn7m2HAM"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"Sherrie Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEm63yRsLn55wvKoeIFLS4hAzKwAZ68pwtU87wApXYj4tL7io=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"‚Ä¢ coffee is okay, nothing special
‚Ä¢ overlooking view of manila bay and moa eye
‚Ä¢ alfresco dining only, best to come at night","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9c9O0JCnIYGUiuNhAXhCteGUZlfU5DgIXAYXy"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Floyser Ricafrente","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXampog85MkNUjDQogXmZaBQIbesV4eLUJg0tDvYrahQrfG3f_HlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Decently priced coffee for its quality and well placed location. Definitely one of the most aesthetically pleasing cafe in SM MOA and a must try. One of its best hours is near sunset since the heat from the sun isn't that intense and it gives you an amazing view of the sunset.

Coffee is a bit strong but in a good way especially for the Mallow and toasted chips frappe. The white mocha frappe does mellow down the strength of the coffee, but it is still present in the overall flavor.

There was a small hiccup with our order when we specifically ordered "White Mocha Iced" but what we got was "Frappe White Mocha" we wondered why the price was different from what was on the menu.

Overall a great place to have a chat and great coffee without breaking the bank, and would come by again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMp4JAdrOTIxladc0XcqiXakrNgbpxP5fXSBOT5"],"When":"2023-4-9"},{"Name":"Karl Macariza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4X2w7qSjkx0OGMjFwm-EFAdq2tODkF2aXvFke9KGqm_QoFPYf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A nice cafe in a great location. I saw the cafe while strolling around the seaside area of MOA and decided to try it because the exterior and ambiance looked very nice and unique to the area. good for taking Instagram pictures (especially at night or in the afternoon).

The staff were very polite and friendly. They do inform you of what is available or not before ordering. The downside is that the service is quite slow. We waited more than 20 minutes for our drinks and food. It might just be because the place is quite full, though.

Food offerings are quite limited. The only available at that time was this Oreo cheesecake type of cake (not sure of the name). The taste is pleasantly sweet. I ordered a non-coffee-based drink with chocolate chips on it. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jeido Morada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSX-VLer-jwgdEwFONRXGJuU2ch5DMiJXIS9PARQaRZ5X_8q4a=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So far, this is the best SB Reserve and best Starbucks branch that I have been into. From excellent customer service to the nice interior and air conditioning of the place, everything is perfect. Not too crowded, you can really relax and enjoy your snack and sip your coffee peacefully.

Baristas are all nice and welcoming and they will make you feel warm with their welcome. I remember when I was searching for the final mug of Black Siren for me to complete the collection, I ask them if they still have one and unfortunately sold out na dw and they will check if meron pa natira on their storage and I said it‚Äôs okay no need to recheck and when I was about to leave the place, the barista felt sorry and told me na wala na dw talaga yung mug na hinahanap ko, Nagulat ako kasi all this time they keep looking for it pa pala. üòÖ

I highly recommend this Reserve, I always make sure to drop-by here whenever I am in MOA. Please keep your excellent customer service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPlrq2It1Nrb_ag5_EvOys4cKJLLMxsDxgRAGwB"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"david alexander justin hernandez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVX8low9Kc7_70ou7zUysFx6VHUz90LeC93ep0Q1rPDGsxX8QNhXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Second Best Starbucks Place in Moa Area.
Here's my Pointers
-Parking is always available near the bay and on com building
-If this is fully occupied you can go to the other sb which is just one block (five e com)
-There is a wheelchair ramp available for pwd and seniors just outside
-This is a reserve starbucks so more options available
-not that spacious but the space is designed for comfort and gatherings
-its just beside BDO for those seniors who does not know how to use a g-cash as payment
-The atmosphere is pleasant. and they do have a signal here compare to the one near the bay
-There aren‚Äôt as many people here due to its location which is a little bit farther from the mall but you can still walk from there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOep10qJQjKIS4ho7arlM9NyyjKCdNYmy5bIGXQ"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Chris Garin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLTvicWWUXH90_1qqtX6N8u4ooEnHzu7zwHdLPEZK2PTBRMTl7yA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the least crowded Starbucks in the MOA area. It is perfect for slow afternoons where you just want to read a book and disconnect.

Its much farther away from the mall compared to the other SB branches but walking there isnt a hassle.

They dont have any outlets if you need to charge and they dont have wifi. The focus if this branch is for groups to interact and socialize, I guess.

So happy that this exists!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhrFmmee-maHYNQyYnp7dU8rfqSgJMbDohKbG9"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"David Warner Henderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEn6_bI6tOtVxqpwLbSFwFNej2uflxAtfWvyToIlZGqw2SZNlYuw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There were only 4 people working this store at 08:03am.

Waiting for my order to be taken was well slow.

The store itself has a nice feel, very comfortable.

Unfortunately the coffee I did order wasn't available due to no one manning the reserve selection.

Lots of interesting collectable starbucks merchandise

The people who attended this store were all but kind and really believed tailgating behind me in lane should fast track them for their orders.

Soo close they can see me enter my pin on my American Express Platinum CC. Changing that.

Would go back and seat if the time allowed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOx_BGB4MnGtHE85pXipHJbcxKPfoIuwjhEZWly"],"When":"2022-12-24"},{"Name":"Karl ‚ÄúKL GROUP‚Äù Lincuna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcfTNY4ccqNv7d0kUvEvfH3nHL9AN8AX-YGSbsn544cv8C8h4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I love this place too cozy and not suitable for work and school study because they don't have a lot of outlets there; I think they're focused more on socializing than like what other sb stores; however, they don't have many seats even though they are Starbucks Reserve.

All in all, I still love this place. üòá","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnh6t_tnARGz2_qp7w1670BdVv_mmJ581J2_U"],"When":"2023-3-24"},{"Name":"Bayne Parker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXFDUnCN2olqIAa2PphPjaos6cBup30-yGUqnvQuJELe-necVB_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff are amazing and they speak perfect English. Perhaps it's due to the clientele this location serves. Across the street is a spa for members only, and the membership starts at 100k pesos. This Starbucks is very clean and has one CR with no bidet. However, it's clean and completely stocked, so there is no wet floor. There's plenty of seating, and it's comfortable and upscale. As always, at every location I've visited, the drinks and food are consistent in every country.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amir Azman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSar7ksgoAUzE7vNph7mwHssscMt04WBD8Wy3keb2j_tNuYzM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the earliest Starbucks to open in Manila. Quite near to the airport hence quite convenient for those who touched down early to grab morning coffee and breakfast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGljE3Fi7I-aemH92AIPS9D4eGE2IB4v3aoh5-"],"When":"2024-1-17"},{"Name":"Manuel Evangelista Jr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVh2bJyOwK8qKB3b0-WNo_enZj_GKS7-RTdvw1ZmuKcyMFsxrKa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very nice ambient coffee place. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"EnidlareG Gomz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMKYJ2xM6Du5owE2mv1ovVNPSmul9U8RquBKIXLrR4Poyw2oJH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Not so happy with what we ordered.... Pizza was a little bland, too watery un cheese tho' we like the beer dough. Thin crust but it's kinda different... a little off with the fried chicken - parang super used oil ang ginamit as the taste was not so yum.... physical yes, looks delish pero the taste .. no! Gravy was even cold. Something is different.... what I like most was my Salted Caramel Latte. Super like nothing more! And the service was kinda long, they will tell you naman it will take awhile orders to arrive... not coming back here for food... sorry! But coffee pwede pa.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdTY_rg9ZlM4DVxsymAhYAMGUxvAVziwvnNDDA"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Aibi Y.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVh3EpS6W94ywkBZKHUKTsItyohb6kTpIykLp_wAp8jZmzoCohw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I really loved the aesthetics and the ambiance of this place. Loved the lights  so much. Great place to hangout with friends. It was a bit pricey but the foods were really presented well. Loved the taste and the look of the Truffle fries. The Iced Salted Caramel Latte and croffles were really tasty but a bit too sweet for me. Would love to try their pizza next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7w58Q79ehtLFrrjLYTPQVx6GgHk6GCrgVWXMc"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"Ida Ngurah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXC7kd4u8hN-Fh9eq9VkW20VhpVxK6lY-Sa8IQDx-pv3k055Ze2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Confused where to eat and starving, i just decided to come in without checking the reviews. I ordered benedict which is not available, so i have sandwich and salted caramel.

Quite some time waiting the food. It is Ok, but not that special. I managed to eat the big portion of sandwich and chips :)

The cafe is chill. Nice ambience. They dont have wifi. Staffs are friendly as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsCOLVj8afKRnj4yjIfetjAno8uiKa9Ci1Lvzx"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Maria Clarissa Nokom (Kai Nokom)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWd7oUEXMIhUDlf6kmy-W-KHBkjae00FAXac0mBTQM2zW-VyYKOrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ambiance is very welcoming. The staff is attentive and assisted us right away.
We ordered classic pancakes, pork belly bbq rice bowl and lamb harissa (my hubby's order).
The pork belly bbq rice tasted similar to a mildly sweet adobo, the meat is tender, right ratio with rice. The meal is filling that we are just able to eat one piece of the classic pancakes.
The classic pancakes have the right amount of sweetness, loved how the cinnamon doesn't overpower the overall taste of the pancakes, so soft and fluffy - we ate our leftover pancakes at our home.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODQMhXSqoLp4CqTmLcj-CgeSQq4ao_3e6QcNnr"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Mestizong Matthuliz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBtAEgPaiu6AEALAou7_MZE4FHJX3gGVFpvcMQH7iT6ckLXh0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This restaurant made me realize that fried chicken and waffle goes perfectly well together. They offer some popular comfort foods, coffees, and alcoholic drinks. Seems the place is a popular hang out spot on a Friday night. Thus, service took some time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiBt1Marg3HLmGrETFRoREzqn7Xfb6KwN5YKT2"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Keiichiro Okamoto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCoZkNUphtRLQoDM-RD6WwxIWeeN28ZT8otjxLNwBFAKvygPG3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Arrived a little after 10 in the morning. I came specifically for the croissant dough waffles, but unfortunately, they were not available. I ended up ordering a smoothie, which also wasn't available. So, I settled for ordering omelet and sausage. Surprisingly, everything except espresso was not available, which seemed odd for a place promoting various extraction methods. Ended up ordering an iced Americano.

The interior had a nice contrast in layout with low tables, long tables for groups, counter tables, booth seats, and round tables. It had a trendy vibe but lacked coherence in the d√©cor, feeling somewhat cluttered. It seemed more geared towards socializing than focusing on the food. The air conditioning was excellent.

The food arrived in about 10 minutes. It consisted of carbs, meat, eggs, and vegetables, a typical breakfast menu. The waffle was terrible, resembling Binangkal more than a waffle. I thought it might be a typical pancake batter substitute, but it was worse than expected.

However, the sausage was exceptionally delicious. It had a great flavor, balance of herbs, oil content, and size, absolutely perfect. The omelet was standard, made with milk, salt, and butter, and the salad was typical with grainy mustard sauce.

The coffee could have been better with higher quality beans.

The sausage was really good. I might revisit for that. If they have it next time, I'd like to try the croissant waffles.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ69ICxIyRlokzZBan_NNi01FgYvZ23ZCQzoSr"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"A Laz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw2saUOg4VU0DPWvx4sxWz6ddoJLMGQQUKyPiaSK1hXXPYs8I53A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Good cafe that serves great coffee. The place was laid back with not too much people in the morning but I wish the servers were more attentive to all the customers. I dined alone and they wouldn't even assist me or give me eye contact.

Picollo coffee was commendable. Will I dine here again? Probably not. Will opt for another resto cafe with better service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMq6Rvo4DB8Ybzv3AriQ6BhIwE-qpP_j9QssXtX"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Kathleen Estrellado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQxNmu5Ykm5_N1_x1QygSA0WvTggdAN_J-Z7CkMfVVd7KT9kA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We swung by for coffee and dessert after dinner, around 9 PM. The restaurant was pretty chill, not too crowded. The atmosphere was really relaxed, which I liked. Service was alright. As for the food, we went for croffles and coffee. They were tasty but on the pricey side.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0SIC3LUm-zqIHnUp5qMqo3HFSPFHpWbGMt0o"],"When":"2024-3-24"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Yoda Travels","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5gHf58wVLJDH9HIhaOBrdv3Zt09Kit36sSk70dc6AXgGafQxu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have no problem with their Coffee and Sandwiches, but the queque is long, the serving time takes longer and the temperature in the area is not comfortable, it's not suprising since the problem with the a.c. here is not a new issue. We need to also wait for available seats, since the place is full, many passengers tends to stay longer while waiting for their flights leaving others standing to wait.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZRRXcwxBaSeWAm2hQs0y3Egyv_UD5SQoFP9eU"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Ding Mark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWD-1dTq2kuF3VhBAVDY1AbnVgnelxz8llKFdg-uXMHJI31bSwa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This branch is behind the customs and not far from the customs since terminal 1 is pretty small. The air conditioner for it is not strong and hot when it‚Äôs crowded.

I order the hot latte and vegetarian frittata for my breakfast so that I can be ready for my morning flights. They are as good as it is.

Since it is one of the busiest and good business in the terminal, maybe should not expect too much on their services.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSU-Txz9GyY-YVxCcOppE38DyuSQS_F5T5hSst"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Paul","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkfy4TFdWV7r0vYhMdsCWdbnHukShlPuMMbzYrdTFV32KuElWL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Airport Starbucks. Cash, credit card and e-wallet payments accepted. Ambiance is not as good as at some other airport Starbucks, but there is a seating area in the back. Larger than usual selection of food items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFvpWHTot9TIjBDyb50hHD0eh3zfCYiYksS5b2"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Jeevan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4YfdXPzD3xWgdcIpEZRzrR1RldhNkT5nVU-UU5gw7ksowFLG_tg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Been here 3 times this year, mostly a hit with the food and how the service flows.

Everything is restocked well which is always a challenge for an airport store.

The one star I am removing for lacking the usual warmth of receiving and serving that is expected from a Starbucks store.

There were several ocassions where an opportunity to connect was missed and they were not even busy.

Overall the best store in this miserable airport terminal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSdtsgdQQqrqRLE4LYZYKfqCAyxA1peHzXhpFW"],"When":"2023-10-14"},{"Name":"LeWayne Ballard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQzNcyGYb6l-ZRwqbwQbIkgYw_7uDCrWhayHblYVZ0Z3oGaWy-Pw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stopped here for a quick drink and snack while waiting for my departure flight.  Line wasn't long and drinks were coming out quickly.  Had the usual hot & cold coffees & teas as well as small snacks found at other Starbucks. There was a small amount of seats available, but most were getting their orders to go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvoV_dhgNYiZY3N0UDGoW3bAOEZ2GoU2TccKzy"],"When":"2023-4-11"},{"Name":"Sansan Chichi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJZ9jYAajjcTW-pP2qzdtVMT-wxr2EmPCXYxshR19hTsNdPFk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The turnover of people is fast so we can usually find a space here to wait for our flight. for travelers looking for a regular meter taxi, their queue is a few steps from here (",)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMM4rOEq60MC82BGydhYUlRmxzP-5m2ws082ohr"],"When":"2023-8-22"},{"Name":"Francesca Ysabel Sales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCAUn1TRBFqbNgZUUTeaYCyZRfZRSJ6GHbgwJLbffqI286o34=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Breakfast place at NAIA both for passengers & greeters (people who fetch their relatives/friends from the airport). Had to book a Grabcar from NAIA 1 International Arrival to NAIA 2 Seattle's (Bay 20) for Php 80, as it was a 17 min walk and we had our luggages.

We thought there was no breakfast available at first, because we checked Zomato before we went to the airport and the food menu was not available. When we got there, the menu was also for drinks only, but thankfully, when we asked the cashier upon ordering, panini breakfast sandwiches (ham & cheese, tomato, salmon & 1 other panini) were available. Got to order my favorite salmon & cream cheese panini.

Inside cafe for small groups (max 8 people), but outside seating were comfortable to sit in at the time we went as well (5 am).

So glad we're able to find a breakfast place at NAIA that's open 24 hrs, and accessible even to greeters. Thank you Seattle's NAIA!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjrrl7zKrG8N1NehDG89lEvGcc6QFfgKod6Wwy"],"When":"2019-11-24"},{"Name":"Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoKinm1O072-7Hxp5_JEHARfHh3R0Uiy2M_3M2viQ7Mv3ObAxh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Iced latte and cinnamon rolls were good.
